cloud-architecture-diagram

title AI-Powered PDF Chat Service Architecture

User Interface [icon: aws-amplify] {
  Web App [icon: azure]
}

AWS Services [icon: aws] {
  API Gateway [icon: aws-api-gateway]
  Lambda Functions [icon: aws-lambda] {
    Vectorize PDF [icon: aws-lambda]
    Query Vector DB [icon: aws-lambda]
    Fetch Text Chunks [icon: aws-lambda]
    Chat Session Handler [icon: aws-lambda]
  }
  Vector Database [icon: aws-neptune]
  Text Storage [icon: aws-s3]
}

OpenAI Services [icon: gcp] {
  Embedding API [icon: openai]
  Chat API [icon: openai]
}

// Connections
Web App > API Gateway
API Gateway > Lambda Functions
Vectorize PDF > Vector Database
Vectorize PDF > Text Storage
Query Vector DB > Vector Database
Fetch Text Chunks > Text Storage
Chat Session Handler > Chat API
Chat Session Handler > Fetch Text Chunks
Embedding API > Vectorize PDF
Embedding API > Query Vector DB
